The industry executives cautioned Trump that the return to normalcy will be anything but swift.
Trump was told “the economy will look very different and operations will look very different,” one participant said.
Larry Hogan said Trump has appointed some “smart people” to his task force who could offer state leaders helpful guidelines as they negotiate the way forward.